          <li>詳細は<a class="c-Link_Txt-inline u-Adjust_Pr-8" href="<%= sitepath %>terms/pdf/rakuten_mobile_applecare_services.pdf" target="_blank">「故障紛失保証 with AppleCare Services 」利用規約<span class="c-Icon_Pdf-l u-Adjust_Pl-24" style="color: #ff008c;"></span></a>をご確認ください。</li>
